    <section id="research">
      <h2 class="section-title">Research Experience</h2>
      <div class="card">
        <p>
          My work covers stellar astrophysics with emphasis on spectroscopy, photometry, binary systems,
          spectral energy distribution (SED) analysis, and stellar evolution.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>My place in the profession:</strong> I contribute as a young researcher who combines
          observational data, computational tools, and publication-driven analysis.
          I develop strong practical workflows and collaborate across institutions on modern astrophysical problems.
        </p>
